PNI
===

PNI stands for Perl Node Interface.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

To install PNI module plus a basic set of PNI nodes, do:
    
    $ cpan PNI::Core

INFO

Point your browser to http://perl-node-interface.blogspot.com .

